    %h3 Our Story
    .story
      %p MemeOverflow is the brainchild of Fab Mackojc, a rising developer from Devbootcamp's Spring 2013 class. Originally conceived as <a href="http://dbcmemes.com">dbcmemes.com</a>, it gained popularity as a novelty app raising happiness and laughter levels from Dev Bootcamp San Franscisco to Chicago. In order to account for the rising hockey curve in user engagement, an all-star team of 4 was formed to build the next generation in memes. Over the course of a few days our team hacked and launched a product that will probably decrease productivity at Dev Bootcamp. Stay for a few laughs and <a href="http://github.com/fmackojc/memeoverflow">help us ship all the memes</a>.
